<template><div><h1 id="is-unc-path" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#is-unc-path" aria-hidden="true">#</a> is-unc-path <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/is-unc-path" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/v/is-unc-path.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM version"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://npmjs.org/package/is-unc-path" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/dm/is-unc-path.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM monthly downloads"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://npmjs.org/package/is-unc-path" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/dt/is-unc-path.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM total downloads"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://travis-ci.org/jonschlinkert/is-unc-path" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/travis/jonschlinkert/is-unc-path.svg?style=flat&amp;label=Travis" alt="Linux Build Status"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h1>
<blockquote>
<p>Returns true if a filepath is a windows UNC file path.</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="install" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#install" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Install</h2>
<p>Install with <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">npm<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>:</p>
<div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> --save is-unc-path
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="usage" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#usage" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Usage</h2>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">var</span> isUncPath <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token function">require</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'is-unc-path'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>true</strong></p>
<p>Returns true for windows UNC paths:</p>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'\\/foo/bar'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'\\\\foo/bar'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'\\\\foo\\admin$'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'\\\\foo\\admin$\\system32'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'\\\\foo\\temp'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'\\\\/foo/bar'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'\\\\\\/foo/bar'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>false</strong></p>
<p>Returns false for non-UNC paths:</p>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'/foo/bar'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'/'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'/foo'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'/foo/'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'c:'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'c:.'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'c:./'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'c:./file'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'c:/'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token function">isUncPath</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'c:/file'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>Customization</strong></p>
<p>Use <code v-pre>.source</code> to use the regex as a component of another regex:</p>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">var</span> myRegex <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">RegExp</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>isUncPath<span class="token punctuation">.</span>source <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">'foo'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong><a href="http://resources.esri.com/help/9.3/ArcGISDesktop/com/Gp_ToolRef/sharing_tools_and_toolboxes/pathnames_explained_colon_absolute_relative_unc_and_url.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Rules for UNC paths<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The computer name is always preceded by a double backward-slash (<code v-pre>\\</code>).</li>
<li>UNC paths cannot contain a drive letter (such as <code v-pre>D:</code>)</li>
</ul>
